name: CaptchaFace-Android
tagline: Captchaface SDK reinvents mobile security by ensuring users of an app are real.
body:
### Welcome to CaptchaFace SDK Pages.
Captchaface reinvents mobile security by ensuring users of an app is real. If you ever need to secure content or simply control the submission of a form, Captchaface will ask users to move their head and show emotions to prove they are real humans.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
